{"tid":1527081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請冷氣軍師搞清楚！是日目的並非停飛！！","createTime":"2019-09-01T08:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T08:58:25.000Z","uid":60544,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a112d929fc18796cb25e27924bcae5f1d2f7bb42","tid":1527081,"uid":60544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:50:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">推我上去呀！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n今日入機場目的係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">「機場交通壓力測試」</span></strong>！<br />\n並<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔係要令飛機停飛！</span></strong>！！<br />\n<br />\n冷氣軍師唔好再叫手足翻入機場！<br />\n目的係癱瘓交通，已經做到！唔係次次都要陣地架！<br />\n<br />\n有以下幾個原因希望大家be water：<br />\n1）<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">機場有禁制令，手足入唔到T1大堂</span></strong><br />\n冇得入大堂 = 冇得搭機鐵，即使機鐵往香港邊向冇停，手足都搭唔到！其次，巴士近乎停哂，如果啲狗真係喺巴士站推入去，手足完全冇路退<br />\n<br />\n2）<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">機場地理位置棘手</span></strong><br />\n分析到口臭喇呢個，今日一早啲狗就喺橋截車查車，如果手足真係死守機場，分分鐘坐定定等拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以請大家適時離開！你估彈出又彈入唔辛苦架咩<br />\n<br />\n3）留得青山在<br />\n大家仲有聽日罷工同更遠既路，唔好死守同陣地，令啲狗狗有機可乘！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">不割𥱊，不分化！<br />\n目標一致，槍口對準黑警政權！<br />\n9.3 大罷工！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b61c0e4452488c57571ccec4aa7fcd7a3b4fd7","tid":1527081,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:50:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"264fe011896d6f8f0b6fc86d6149f466c3652938","tid":1527081,"uid":60544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"23145d1bdd19d80e393f98bbf16b4ec676200734","tid":1527081,"uid":60544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep